rows.label: tlk41300072_02_msg0001
rows.name:
I hear the goddess of
the Holy See is dead.

rows.label: tlk41300072_02_msg0002
rows.name:
Isn't this just payback for
managing Blades and distributing
them to Superbia and Invidia?

rows.label: tlk41300072_02_msg0003
rows.name:
...Oops, I shouldn't say
such things. Please pretend
you didn't hear that.

rows.label: tlk41300072_02_msg0004
rows.name:
The rations we get here
were continued thanks to
the goddess, after all.
